&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-golang" data-lang="golang">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// Task 接口类型
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kd">type&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">Task&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">interface&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nf">Exec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">error&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// TaskA Task接口的实现类A
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kd">type&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">TaskA&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">struct&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">A&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">`json:&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">ta&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">TaskA&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">Exec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">error&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">fmt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Println&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;TaskA Exec&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">nil&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// TaskB Task接口的实现类B
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kd">type&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">TaskB&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">struct&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">B&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">string&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">`json:&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kd">func&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">tb&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">TaskB&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">Exec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">error&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">fmt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Println&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;TaskB Exec&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">nil&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// MixedStruct 反序列化目标结构体
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kd">type&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">MixedStruct&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kd">struct&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">Id&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">uint64&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">`json:&amp;#34;id&amp;#34;`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">Task&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">Task&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">`json:&amp;#34;task&amp;#34;`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>MySQL where 范围查询和 order by 关键字无法同时命中索引</title><link>http://weirwei.cn/practical/index_in_orderby/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Sep 2023 15:18:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://weirwei.cn/practical/index_in_orderby/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
 &lt;p>开发中，使用 in 和 order by 的时候，发现无法同时命中索引。&lt;/p>

 &lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>使用 &lt;code>IN&lt;/code> 运算符来过滤行时，&lt;code>MySQL&lt;/code> 会先使用索引来定位表中的行，并将这些行的所有数据读入内存中。随后，&lt;code>MySQL&lt;/code> 会根据查询语句中的 &lt;code>ORDER BY&lt;/code> 子句对这些数据进行排序。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Gorm 的黑魔法</title><link>http://weirwei.cn/practical/gorm_black_magic/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Sep 2023 15:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://weirwei.cn/practical/gorm_black_magic/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
 &lt;p>小伙看到同事写的Gorm黑魔法，逐渐不淡定了。&lt;/p>

 &lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>开发过程中，看到同事的代码写了这么一段：&lt;/p>

&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-1">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-1">1&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-2">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-2">2&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-3">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-3">3&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-4">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-4">4&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-5">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-5">5&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-6">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-6">6&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt" id="hl-0-7">&lt;a class="lnlinks" href="#hl-0-7">7&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-go" data-lang="go">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">Session&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">gorm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Session&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Context&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Statement&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Context&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">}).&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">FirstOrCreate&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">entity&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Error&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">!=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kc">nil&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">components&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">ErrorDbInsert&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">WrapPrintf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Error&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;Insert error, entity:%s&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">utils&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nf">ToJson&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">entity&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">db&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">RowsAffected&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">components&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">ErrorAlreadyExist&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>go test 的内联问题</title><link>http://weirwei.cn/practical/inlining/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Sep 2023 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://weirwei.cn/practical/inlining/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
 &lt;p>使用&lt;code>monkey&lt;/code>对函数进行打桩单测的时候，发现打桩函数没有生效。&lt;/p>

 &lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>习惯直接使用IDE的可视化的&lt;code>run&lt;/code>和&lt;code>debug&lt;/code>功能进行跑单测，没有关注到具体执行的命令。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>